<div id="home">

<p>I am a <a href="/work/index.html">freelance writer</a>. I live in Buffalo, NY. I write for the web, I write books, co-host podcasts, and help launch events.</p>

<p>You can find me online at <a href="https://twitter.com/kevinpurdy">Twitter</a> , <a href="http://kevinpurdy.tumblr.com/">Tumblr</a>, <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/+KevinPurdy">Google+</a>, and <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/purdman1">Flickr</a>. If you're in Buffalo, you might find me at <a href="http://coworkbuffalo.com">CoworkBuffalo</a> or walking <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/purdman1/tags/howard/">Howard</a>.</p>

